if {family_response} == "help":
	player_character: You pull out the photo the desperate potato gave you. His wife. [color=STEEL_BLUE]Where is she now?[/color] #id:235
	player_character: If what Sasha and Murphy are saying is true... she's already been... #id:236
	audio "res://assets/audio/stings/revelation_dark.mp3" [volume="-8.0" bus="SFX"]
	player_character: You can't finish the thought. But you [color=CHARTREUSE]won't forget her face[/color]. #id:237

player_character: Tomorrow, everything changes. Either you find answers, or you bury the questions forever. #id:238
player_character: One thing is certain: there's [color=YELLOW]no going back to blissful ignorance[/color]. #id:239
